<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>lḥẓẗ slạm</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạḥtạrwạ ktyr fy ạmry wqạlwạ ʿlyạ klạm bḍyʿ kl ʿmry wʿạysẖ fy ạlạwhạm wạnạ gẖrqạn fy ạlkẖṭyẗ wḥyạty mnthyẗ wbṣrkẖlk yạrby qwyny ạmsk ạydyạ ạlqrạr - qwyny yạrby byk qwyny wạskn fyạ nsyny ạlmạḍy klh wạmsḥ dmʿẗ ʿnyạ 2- wbyzyd ạlklạm wtsẖtd ạlạlạm msẖ mṭmn wkẖạyf mḥtạj lḥẓẗ slạm wạnạ bndhlk tʿạly gẖyr ḥạlty ạlmḥạlẗ wạrfʿny mn ạlkẖṭyẗ ạlly ḍlt ʿynyạ 3- ạnạ knt fy dnyạ tạyh wmsẖftsẖ ywm ạmạn ʿly nạr ạbdyẗ rạyḥ wfy gẖyrhạ mlysẖ mkạn wktyr mn ʿmry rạḥ wạnạ ʿạysẖ fy ạljrạḥ wlqyt qlby ạlgẖryq mḥtạj ylqy ạlṭryq 4- kẖlyny ạnsạn jdyd frḥạn qlby sʿyd rjʿny lḥḍn qlbk wạʿysẖ yạ yswʿ fy ḥbk</lyrics>
<author>rwmạny ḥlmy̱, rwmạny ḥlmy̱</author>
